OL,3,CHillsborough Law update 'coming
OL,4,Cimminently' as 36th anniversary
OL,5,Capproaches
OL,7,FAn update on the long-awaited
OL,8,F'Hillsborough Law' is expected soon,
OL,9,Ffollowing reports a meeting between
OL,10,Fthe Prime Minister and campaigners was
OL,11,Fcancelled, amid concerns it will be
OL,12,Fwatered down.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer pledged at the Labour
OL,15,Fparty conference last year that such a
OL,16,Flaw will be introduced in Parliament
OL,17,Fbefore the 36th anniversary of the
OL,18,FHillsborough disaster, which will be
OL,19,Fmarked on April 15 this year.
