OL,7,FLast week it was reported that a
OL,8,Fmeeting between Sir Keir and
OL,9,Fcampaigners had been cancelled, with
OL,10,Fclaims officials were attempting to
OL,11,Fhave the contents of a bill watered
OL,12,Fdown.
OL,14,FIt is understood concerns relate to
OL,15,Fwho the duty of candour would apply to.
