OL,3,CHillsborough Law update 'coming
OL,4,Cimminently' as 36th anniversary
OL,5,Capproaches
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice said the Government is "fully
OL,9,Fcommitted to bringing in a
OL,10,FHillsborough Law which will include a
OL,11,Flegal duty of candour for public
OL,12,Fservants and criminal sanctions for
OL,13,Fthose who refuse to comply".
OL,15,FBuilding safety minister Alex Norris
OL,16,Fsaid there will be an update "coming
OL,17,Fimminently".
