OL,7,FHe told MPs at the Housing,
OL,8,FCommunities and Local Government
OL,9,FCommittee on Tuesday: "I know that
OL,10,Fthere is a lot of interest in the
OL,11,FHillsborough Law and the implications
OL,12,Ffor the duty of candour. In
OL,13,Fpreparation for this session, it
OL,14,Fprobably won't surprise you, I was
OL,15,Fasking colleagues about the status of
OL,16,Fthat, I believe that's coming
OL,17,Fimminently.
