OL,7,F"I can't speak to where that then
OL,8,Ffinishes for the piece of work on the
OL,9,Foversight mechanism, because that is a
OL,10,FCabinet Office-led one.
OL,12,F"But those calls have been understood,
OL,13,Fand it will be addressed in the future
OL,14,Fin terms of what model the
OL,15,FGovernment's choosing going forwards."
OL,17,FCampaigners on a range of scandals
OL,18,Fincluding the Grenfell fire and
OL,19,Finfected blood victims have also
OL,20,Fpreviously called for an independent
OL,21,Fpublic body to be put in place.
