OL,7,FThis would be responsible for
OL,8,Fcollating, analysing and following up
OL,9,Fon recommendations from public
OL,10,Finquiries.
OL,12,FThey have argued that, without such a
OL,13,Fbody in place, governments can delay
OL,14,Fthe implementation of, or even ignore
OL,15,Fentirely, recommendations from public
OL,16,Finquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
