OL,7,FAt the committee session, which
OL,8,Fcovered a range of topics including
OL,9,Fthe Government's response to the final
OL,10,Freport of the Grenfell Tower Inquiry,
OL,11,FMr Norris said he recognised the call
OL,12,Ffor an oversight mechanism, from
OL,13,Fcampaigners who have been victim of
OL,14,F"scandal and failure of the British
OL,15,Fstate".
OL,17,FHowever, he added that the Grenfell
OL,18,Finquiry report had stopped short of
OL,19,Frecommending such a mechanism.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@FO]
