OL,7,FHe told MPs: "For my part in it, the
OL,8,Frecommendation in the inquiry stopped
OL,9,Fat a publicly accessible database. We
OL,10,Fare delivering that.
OL,12,F"We've promised quarterly reporting on
OL,13,Fgov.uk and an annual session in
OL,14,Fparliament for colleagues to
OL,15,Fscrutinise us."
OL,17,FAsked directly by Conservative MP
OL,18,FLewis Cocking whether the Government
OL,19,Fis going to introduce a national
OL,20,Foversight mechanism, Mr Norris said he
OL,21,F"can't make that commitment".
