OL,7,FHe added: "That's a Cabinet Office-run
OL,8,Fprocess. I've made the commitment I've
OL,9,Fmade in line with what we published in
OL,10,Fthe inquiry on the publicly available
OL,11,Finformation. The work is ongoing
OL,12,Facross Government on the national
OL,13,Foversight mechanism more generally."
OL,15,FThe Cabinet Office has been contacted
OL,16,Ffor comment.
